American singer and dancer, Chris Brown, has shared a picture he took withNigerian music superstar, Davido. Chris Brown, who previously collaborated with another Nigerian music superstar, Wizkid, posted the picture on Instagram on Thursday. The photo is in anticipation of the release a new single by the American star titled “Blow my mind” along with Davido. While sharing the artwork of the single last week, he had written: “Coming soon!”